sources.title: INVADERS FROM SPACE
sources.description: Starman aka Supergiant once again comes to Earth to save us from space aliens. This is the weirdest of the 4 English dubbed Starman/Supergiant imports.

sources.title: Invaders From Space (1965)
sources.description: The last of the STARMAN (SUPERGIANT in Japan) features from USA producer Walter Manley, edited together from the 1950s Japanese TV advetures. This MPEG2 file is better in quality than the previous upload of this feature already on IA.

sources.title: Invaders from Space (1965) STARMAN
sources.description:
Stars: Ken Utsui, Minako Yamada, Junko Ikeuchi
 Directors: Koreyoshi Akasaka, Teruo Ishii

 A bunch of pernicious salamander men from the planet Kulimon in the Moffit Galaxy plan on taking over Earth by unleashing a lethal plague on mankind. It's up to valiant superhero Starman from the Emerald Planet to save the human race before it's too late.
